2017年9月22日傍晚，一輛行走[[城巴E21A線|E21A線]]的[[亞歷山大丹尼士Enviro_500_MMC|亞歷山大丹尼士Enviro 500 MMC]] 12米巴士（車隊編號8515，車牌號碼TF5883）往[[愛民巴士總站|愛民]]方向行駛，駛至長沙灣道近欽州街交界時，疑收掣不及，失控鏟上行人路，上層左邊車頭更被大廈簷蓬劏開。由於正值繁忙時間，多名途人走避不及被捲進車底，造成3死近30人受傷。<ref>[http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170922/bkn-20170922185210157-0922_00822_001.html 城巴剷行人路簷篷劏車頭 途人捲車底3死29傷] {{Wayback|url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170922/bkn-20170922185210157-0922_00822_001.html |date=20200405082814 }}，東方報業集團網站，2017-09-22</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1669488-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%96%91%E6%92%9E%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%89%B7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%AF+%E7%8B%82%E5%B7%B4%E5%99%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%91%BD+%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA%E6%8D%B2%E8%BB%8A%E5%BA%95 |title=疑撞的士剷行人路 狂巴噬三命 途人捲車底 |date=2017-09-23 |work=星島日報 |accessdate=2018-12-11 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609110635/http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1669488-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%96%91%E6%92%9E%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%89%B7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%AF+%E7%8B%82%E5%B7%B4%E5%99%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%91%BD+%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA%E6%8D%B2%E8%BB%8A%E5%BA%95 |dead-url=no }}</ref>肇事巴士司機被控危險駕駛導致他人死亡罪及危險駕駛引致他人嚴重受傷罪，判囚30個月，停牌5年，並須自費參加駕駛改進課程。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.hk01.com/article/269126/ |title=城巴剷上行人路 司機被判囚2年半　死者家屬哭訴：判得咁輕 |date=2018-12-10 |work=香港01 |accessdate=2018-12-11 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912143227/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/269126/%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%B4%E5%89%B7%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%AF-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A2%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A-%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%93%AD%E8%A8%B4-%E5%88%A4%E5%BE%97%E5%92%81%E8%BC%95 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
